tech%20sector%20is%20now%2037%25%20of%20the%20US%20stock%20market%2C%20surpassing%20the%20dot-com%20era%20peak.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20rising%20bond%20yields%20will%20eventually%20stop%20the%20rally%2C%20Edwards%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20high%20market%20valuation%20levels%20he%20warns%20about%2C%20Soci%C3%A9t%C3%A9%20G%C3%A9n%C3%A9rale%20strategist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-albert-edwards-bubble-bearish-outlook-japan-yields-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlbert%20Edwards%3C%2Fa%3E'%20bearish%20missives%20don't%20tend%20to%20serve%20well%20as%20near-term%20market%20timing%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20acknowledges%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20equity%20investor%20who%20heeded%20my%20words%20of%20caution%20on%20the%20US%20Tech%20'bubble'%20will%20by%20now%20have%20taken%20to%20sticking%20pins%20in%20plasticine%20models%20of%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20wrote%20in%20an%20August%2021%20note%20to%20clients.%20%26quot%3BIndeed%2C%20my%20ankle%20has%20been%20hurting%20for%20over%20six%20months%20and%20although%20the%20physio%20says%20it%20is%20tendonitis%2C%20I%20strongly%20suspect%20otherwise.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20no%20denying%20that%20Edwards%2C%20a%20stark%20contrarian%20amid%20the%20pervasively%20bullish%20attitude%20on%20Wall%20Street%20these%20days%2C%20has%20some%20concerning%20observations%20about%20where%20the%20market%20sits%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20with%20respect%20to%20tech%20stocks%2C%20and%20in%20the%20context%20of%20government%20bond%20yields.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuilding%20on%20his%20argument%20that%20the%20market%20is%20in%20a%20bubble%2C%20he%20highlighted%20in%20his%20latest%20note%20that%20the%20tech%20sector%20now%20makes%20up%2037%25%20of%20the%20total%20US%20market%2C%20which%20is%20higher%20than%20at%20the%20peak%20of%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20in%202000.%20Over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20investors%20have%20piled%20into%20tech%20amid%20the%20frenzied%20excitement%20about%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22tech%20sector%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a8ac91194a2d49b8af07d4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221446%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESOCIETE%20GENERALE%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20metric%20showing%20that%20the%20tech%20sector%20has%20historically%20high%20valuations%20is%20a%20falling%20free%20cash%20flow%20yield.%20This%20means%20that%20current%20market%20prices%20are%20high%20relative%20to%20cash%20flow%20after%20expenses%20as%20tech%20firms%20dump%20money%20into%20AI%20development.%20The%20sector%20has%20a%20free%20cash%20flow%20yield%20of%20around%20two.%20This%20is%20also%20reflected%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20low%20dividend%20yield%20of%201.2%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20long-term%20government%20bond%20yields%20have%20surged%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20the%20tech%20rally%2C%20and%20offer%20virtually%20risk-free%20yields%20of%20over%204%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ratio%20of%2010-year%20Treasury%20yields%20to%20the%20market's%20dividend%20yield%20has%20climbed%20to%20dot-com%20era%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222466%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2210y%20bond%20yield%20vs%20stock%20market%20dividend%20yield%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68a8b3decfc04e97619be1ef%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESOCIETE%20GENERALE%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20rising%20bond%20yields%20have%20weighed%20on%20stock%20valuations%2C%20but%20that%20hasn't%20seemed%20to%20be%20the%20case%20so%20far%20in%20this%20market.%20Edwards%20says%20it's%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20until%20that%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20the%20other%20day%2C%20interest%20rates%20were%20rock%20bottom%20and%20equity%20bulls%20were%20telling%20us%20that%20sky%20high%20equity%20valuations%20were%20justified%20by%20TINA%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EThere%20Is%20No%20Alternative%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20TINA%20magic%20no%20longer%20works%2C%20now%20that%20interest%20rates%20are%20so%20much%20higher.%20So%2C%20how%20come%20the%20equity%20market%20is%20able%20to%20shrug%20off%20the%20relentless%20rise%20in%20long%20bond%20yields%20by%20feeding%20off%20news%20of%20strong%20profits%20from%20a%20handful%20of%20mega-cap%20tech%20stocks%20and%20the%20promise%20of%20more%20to%20come%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSurely%20we%20can%20all%20agree%20that%20rising%20bond%20yields%20will%20break%20the%20equity%20market%20at%20some%20point%3F%20But%20when%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BGoodbye%20to%20the%20post-GFC%20TINA%20world%20when%20equities%20yielded%20almost%20as%20much%20as%20bonds%20and%20hello%20to%20an%20ever%20more%20stretched%20elastic%20band%20which%20will%20surely%20eventually%20snap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBond%20yields%20could%20be%20on%20the%20way%20down%20after%20Federal%20Reserve%20Chair%20Jerome%20Powell%20took%20on%20a%20dovish%20tone%20in%20his%20speech%20in%20Jackson%20Hole%2C%20Wyoming%2C%20on%20Friday.%20Lower%20rates%20are%20typically%20bullish%20for%20stocks%2C%20and%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20rallied%20around%201.5%25%20on%20Friday%20after%20Powell's%20remarks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20remains%20unclear%20how%20much%20the%20central%20bank%20will%20slash%20rates%20in%20the%20year%20ahead%20and%20how%20the%20labor%20market%2C%20consumer%20spending%2C%20and%20inflation%20will%20fare%20as%20the%20economy%20digests%20higher%20tariff%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20for%20now%2C%20as%20he%20wrote%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Edwards%20will%20keep%20wondering%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20big%20could%20this%20bubble%20get%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.busin