C%20supported%20by%20detailed%20instructions.%20Procuring%20native%20cows%20for%20bio-inputs%20was%20another%20struggle%2C%20while%20logistics%20meant%20long%20and%20costly%20journeys%20to%20the%20nearest%20town.%20Introducing%20innovative%20practices%2C%20such%20as%20colour-coded%20wristbands%20for%20harvesting%20ripe%20berries%2C%20helped%20ensure%20quality%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinancially%2C%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20years%20were%20a%20total%20loss%2C%20mainly%20because%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20find%20customers%20who%20truly%20valued%20quality.%20Even%20those%20who%20did%20buy%20often%20failed%20to%20pay%20me.%20That%20difficult%20time%20taught%20me%20an%20important%20lesson%20%E2%80%94%20to%20sell%20only%20to%20customers%20who%20appreciate%20quality%20and%20pay%20upfront.%20This%20decision%20turned%20the%20tables%2C%20and%20from%20the%20third%20year%20onwards%2C%20I%20began%20making%20a%20profit%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20life%20post%20voluntary%20retirement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20Iyer%E2%80%99s%20perseverance%20began%20to%20yield%20results%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F173019%2Fkarnataka-black-baza-coffee-purchase-review-organic-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20plants%20bore%20aromatic%20beans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cardamoms%20released%20their%20fragrance%2C%20and%20black%20pepper%20thrived%20under%20the%20canopy%20of%20organically%20nurtured%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20happiness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Iyer%20thought%2C%20as%20he%20saw%20his%20hard%20work%20manifest%20in%20the%20vibrant%20life%20of%20his%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com