ion%20and%20climate%20stress.%20(Representational%20image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fyoung-indian-farmer-standing-green-millet-2263537057%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShutterstock%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20Dasra%2C%20every%20initiative%20has%20been%20rooted%20in%20collaborative%20action%20with%20communities%20at%20the%20centre.%20Through%20conversations%20with%20diverse%20organisations%2C%20we%20realised%20there%20was%20a%20significant%20gap%20in%20work%20around%20climate.%20This%20pushed%20us%20to%20explore%20it%20from%20an%20intersectional%20lens%2C%20focusing%20on%20strengthening%20community%20resilience.%20The%20aim%20was%20to%20shape%20an%20India%20view%2C%20create%20a%20common%20vocabulary%2C%20and%20enable%20multi-stakeholder%20engagement%20on%20climate%20action%20for%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pranay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20explore%20this%2C%20Dasra%20spoke%20with%20almost%20100%20organisations%20in%20its%20network%20that%20were%20working%20in%20climate-adjacent%20areas%2C%20seeking%20to%20understand%20what%20a%20dedicated%20climate%20alliance%20could%20look%20like.%20They%20already%20knew%20how%20to%20build%20alliances%2C%20but%20they%20wanted%20to%20hear%20directly%20from%20partners%20about%20priorities%20within%20the%20climate%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerged%20from%20these%20conversations%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98ClimateRISE%20Alliance%20(CRA)%E2%80%99%2C%20launched%20in%20early%202023.%20Bringing%20together%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20think%20tanks%2C%20intermediary%20groups%2C%20and%20funders%2C%20the%20CRA%20was%20established%20with%20support%20from%20Rainmatter%20Foundation%2C%20Oak%20Foundation%2C%20and%20MacArthur%20Foundation.%20Its%20aim%20is%20to%20shape%20%E2%80%9Can%20India%20view%E2%80%9D%20on%20intersectional%20climate%20act