haped%20the%20idea%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQwilt%E2%80%99s%20roots%20go%20deeper%20than%20a%20worn-out%20quilt.%20Atharva%20grew%20up%20seeing%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20compassion%20for%20working-class%20women.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20believed%20in%20empowering%20women%20through%20skill%20and%20small%20home-based%20work.%20That%20spirit%20lives%20on%20in%20Qwilt%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20his%20mother%2C%20Vinita%20Rajesh%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20legacy%20was%20reinforced%20at%20home.%20Vinita%20says%20Atharva%E2%80%99s%20father%20always%20encouraged%20open%20dialogue%2C%20a%20habit%20that%20shaped%20his%20ability%20to%20listen%2C%20question%2C%20and%20lead.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20helped%20Atharva%20become%20the%20confident%2C%20empathetic%20leader%20he%20is%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171712.845-1755172127.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Qwilt%20was%20a%20small%20moment%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20save%20a%20missing%20craft%2C%20a%20fading%20tradition%2C%20and%20a%20family%20memory%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20lose%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171712.845-1755172127.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171712.845-1755172127-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171712.845-1755172127-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171712.845-1755172127-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T17171