ood%20for%20many%20women.%20But%20after%20moving%2C%20they%20found%20the%20craft%20had%20almost%20disappeared%20from%20the%20community%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtharva%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20replacing%20the%20quilt.%20It%20was%20about%20reviving%20a%20dying%20tradition%2C%20reducing%20clothing%20waste%2C%20and%20creating%20something%20meaningful.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20circular%20model.%20People%20donate%20old%20%3Cem%3Esarees%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20bedsheets%2C%20and%20fabric.%20We%20teach%20women%20to%20make%20quilts%2C%20and%20then%20we%20gift%20those%20quilts%20to%20those%20who%20need%20them%20most.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%2010%20women%20are%20actively%20engaged%20in%20quilting%20as%20part%20of%20Qwilt.%20They%20are%20compensated%20on%20a%20per-quilt%20basis%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-14T171512.339-1755171930-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-487198%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-cap